  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/espn/status/2034625207571194223",
      "reply_text": "That's a big change of heart. Guess the Lakers' win changed his mind about Vegas.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:04:36.504114+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SaycheeseDGTL/status/2034623942590095521",
      "reply_text": "That's a cool promotion. Fans love swag like that.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:05:09.702147+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TMThreadDiscord/status/2034624382107062753",
      "reply_text": "Luka's been on fire. Can't wait to see him perform again.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:05:51.580032+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ClutchPoints/status/2034624364096684264",
      "reply_text": "That's a testament to his dedication and work ethic.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:06:44.527591+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Basket_Infos/status/2034593227458699573",
      "reply_text": "Comme si on ne savait pas que la compétitivité est le moteur de la réussite en NBA. 🤔",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:07:22.334307+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Fr4noTO/status/2034627368602476939",
      "reply_text": "That's harsh. He's still a rookie.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:08:08.251361+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Yinoma2001/status/2034625057603940784",
      "reply_text": "Fair. Bench units can be a great way to get some young guys minutes and see what they've got.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:08:59.465286+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/thebabc/status/2034603062266904729",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, 4 hours is a lot for a game. That's just the NBA grind.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:09:47.129607+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FT_Merchant05/status/2034624986472698340",
      "reply_text": "Not sure what you're insinuating about Tatum's injury, but he's been playing great this season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:22:17.678880+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BillyReinhardt/status/2034624969724858512",
      "reply_text": "Cade Cunningham's injury is a huge blow to the Pistons. Tough for them to make a deep run now.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:22:49.414903+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/i/status/2034626123305222490",
      "reply_text": "Big milestone for Jaylen. He's making his mark on Celtics history.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:23:24.405037+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JonKrawczynski/status/2034628717876498927",
      "reply_text": "Chemistry matters, but so does his defense. Can he lock down the paint with Rudy?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:44:45.227811+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FireDFS1/status/2034607728170336274",
      "reply_text": "High screens are a problem for him. Agree on that.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:45:15.584825+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/LAbound2/status/2034620182384017885",
      "reply_text": "When he's consistently making life tough for the league's best. That's a good start.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:56:15.696591+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/WalderSports/status/2034638985331449922",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, but they still gotta hold it together. One slip and they're out of the playoff mix.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:57:03.474285+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/sidjustkidding/status/2034630219814846934",
      "reply_text": "Eastern conference is a mess this year. Good luck with those plans.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T14:57:34.426947+00:00"
    }
  ],
